https://www.npmjs.com/package/live-server

This is a little development server with live reload capability. Use it for hacking your HTML/JavaScript/CSS files, but not for deploying the final site.
Olhar o resto da explicação no site, bem interessante (servidor http com live reload).



npm install -g live-server


Live-server sem o package Json
npm install live-server
./node_modules/live-server/live-server.js --help
./node_modules/live-server/live-server.js --host=localhost --port=8080